{
  "ref": "durrik",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "Durrik",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "First time",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Don't think I've met you before. You here to buy?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Buy what?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "All sorts of things."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Why are you selling things in a cave?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "A dwarf has to make a living."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Are you not getting paid?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "To mine? Of course. Still, no harm in having multiple sources of income, is there?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I guess not."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Exactly. So, what are you buying?"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Subsequent times",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "What are you buying?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What are you selling?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "See for yourself."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Where do you get the things that you sell?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Does it matter?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I'm just curious."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Well, I have my methods."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "That's not much of an answer."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "That's the way around here."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What does that mean?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Does it have to mean anything?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Well... yes. Otherwise why would you have said it?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Alright then, riddle me this: Why are we here?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Is that some sort of existential question, or...?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "I suppose it could be, but I was specifically referring to this place. Why are we here?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "To mine?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "For?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Ore?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "So they say. Plenty of ore elsewhere though."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "If you're not here for ore, then why are you here?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Ah, but I can't answer that. Besides, even if I could, it would ruin the riddle. You'll just have to keep pondering it for yourself. Now, what are you buying?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Nothing, thanks."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Durrik",
                  "text": "Suit yourself."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    }
  ]
}